{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.error()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/error","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/debug\"><code>debug()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/group\"><code>group()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/info\"><code>info()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/profile\"><code>profile()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/trace\"><code>trace()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Console API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>向 Web 控制台输出一条错误消息。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.error(<em>obj1</em> [, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN</em>]);\nconsole.error(<em>msg</em> [, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN</em>]);\nconsole.exception(<em>obj1</em> [, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN</em>]);\nconsole.exception(<em>msg</em> [, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN</em>]);\n</pre>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> <code>console.exception()</code> 是 <code>console.error() 的别名；它们功能相同。</code></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj1\"><code>obj1</code> ... <code>objN</code></dt>\n <dd>要输出的 JavaScript 对象列表。这些对象的字符串形式按顺序加起来然后输出。</dd>\n <dt id=\"msg\"><code>msg</code></dt>\n <dd>一个字符串，它包含零个或多个替代字符串。</dd>\n <dt id=\"subst1\"><code>subst1</code> ... <code>substN</code></dt>\n <dd>JavaScript 对象可以用此来替换<code>msg</code>里的替代字符串。你可以控制输出的格式。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>详情请看<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a>文档中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console#outputting_text_to_the_console\">输出文本到控制台</a> 。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#error","title":"Console Standard"}],"query":"api.console.error"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.console.error","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/error/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/gg589530\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN: Using the F12 Tools Console to View Errors and Status</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/chrome-developer-tools/docs/console#errors_and_warnings\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chrome Developer Tools: Using the Console</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"向 Web 控制台输出一条错误消息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"console.error()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"console.error()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.error()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.error()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.error()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.error()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"console.error()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/console/error","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/console/error/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console","title":"Console"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console/error","title":"Console.error()"}],"pageTitle":"Console.error() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}